    "Name": "Zeus",
    "Details": "Armor for the -13S is a hefty fifteen tons of standard armor, fully 97% of the theoretical maximum for an 80-ton BattleMech. Primary weapons include an ER PPC, an ER Large Laser and  an Ultra AC 20. Rounding out this impressive array is a single Medium Pulse Laser for close-in work on infantry and battle armor. The -13S is intended to close at top speed in battalion strength, firing all the way, deploying in a 'hedgehog' formation which ensures many of this design will reach their opponents untouched. Seventeen Double Heat Sinks guarantee the pilot can sustain maximum fire without any heat issues. None of the weapons has a minimum range. Once into the Ultra AC 20's short or medium range, the pilot merely disengages his ER Large Laser, slaves the Ultra AC 20 in its place and continues firing.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Barrel Fist</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.14</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Right Upper</color>",
